    Test, if cleaning up works properly.

    This agent starts plans, which try to provoke memory leaks. The test(s) to run can be selected: 1=goals, 2=conditions, 3=internal events, 4=message events, 0=all tests. todo: how to determine success of testcases? memory consumption is not meaningful
